cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CE, cs.SY 

The paper discusses the use of machine learning algorithms for classification in high energy physics, specifically focusing on feature construction using Genetic Programming. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the use of Genetic Programming involves optimization techniques (cs.NE) and the enforcement of dimensional consistency using grammars involves computational engineering (cs.CE) and systems and control (cs.SY).
